# Task Tracker (Python + JSON)

## Project URL
https://roadmap.sh/projects/task-tracker

## Description
This project is a simple **Task Tracker CLI application** built using **Python**.  
It allows users to manage tasks using a **JSON file as storage**.

The application supports basic CRUD operations:
- Add tasks
- View tasks
- Update tasks
- Update task status
- Delete tasks

Each task stores:
- Task ID
- Title
- Description
- Status (Todo / In Progress / Done)
- Created Date
- Updated Date

The data is stored locally in a **tasks.json** file.

---

## Features
- Add new tasks
- View all tasks
- Update task details
- Update task status
- Delete tasks
- Track creation and update date
- Menu-driven CLI interface

---

## Technologies Used
- Python
- JSON
- File Handling
- Datetime module

---

